m', 'Estradiol', 'Vincristine, Cabazitaxel, Vinblastine, Topotecan, Teniposide, Irinotecan, Vinorelbine, Etoposide', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/25604/', '[1] "Product Information. Yondelis (trabectedin)." Janssen Pharmaceuticals, Titusville, NJ.[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[3] "Product Information. Yondelis (trabectedin)." Janssen Pharmaceuticals, Titusville, NJ.[4] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0', 1767369485);
